                    <p>We provide education materials, scholarships, and training for communities in need.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="program-card">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Program 2">
                    <h3>Healthcare Support</h3>
                    <p>We offer medical assistance, disease prevention programs, and healthcare facilities.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="program-card">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Program 3">
                    <h3>Economic Empowerment</h3>
                    <p>We help individuals develop skills for sustainable livelihoods and financial stability.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Get Involved Section -->
    <section class="get-involved">
        <h2>Get Involved</h2>
        <p>Join us in creating lasting change in the communities we serve. Your support makes a world of difference.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="cta-btn">Donate Now</a>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h4>About Us</h4>
                <p>We are a non-profit organization committed to improving lives through education, healthcare, and economic empowerment.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h4>Quick Links</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
